{"tid":510124,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"摩佬念亡父：最難捱的聖誕","createTime":"2017-12-26T06:53:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-26T07:28:32.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a9100698a3a45148284c87584c7d55b5edc29bc6","tid":510124,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T06:53:37.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=WopXK2SOPlMnIw00Z1swJJZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=f8908715\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】曼聯領隊摩連奴坦言，父親早前離世，令今年聖誕節不再快樂。<br />\n<br />\n「這是我首次在沒有父親的情況下過聖誕節，我認為今年是我人生最難過的聖誕節。」摩連奴（Jose Mourinho）的父親於今年6月因病去世，而摩佬其後特意返回家鄉塞圖巴爾，為父親抬棺及舉辦追思會。<br />\n<br />\n菲力士也是個足球人，球員生涯司職門將，為維多利亞及比蘭倫斯2支葡萄牙球會，上陣超過270場，而且曾1次代表葡萄牙國家隊披甲；退役後，他踢而優則教，20年執教日子裡，帶領過11支球隊。<br />\n<br />\n日子難過也要過，曼聯在拆禮物日迎戰般尼，之後接連在主場鬥修咸頓，以及作客愛華頓，再於英足盃第3圈撼來訪的打比郡，相信這樣頻繁的賽程，可以令摩佬分分心，不會太過思念亡父。"},{"pid":"32f575a743218f76a5c106cc46851eb5c8179dec","tid":510124,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T06:53:47.000Z","msg":"Daddy<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cb1a6ae70997b9d984de33802ceb16b9109552c","tid":510124,"uid":49859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T06:58:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9d3ec4e6de2224f729d85887c510ec6271209e9","tid":510124,"uid":35365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T07:14:15.000Z","msg":"班衰仔前晚仲要踢場垃圾波出黎激daddy<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a23c9ab114466f1e1eefe30395ca5477fee6fcb5","tid":510124,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T07:16:50.000Z","msg":"爺爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a2db004a6ab5d7fd331a09f5e05538802890f26","tid":510124,"uid":23385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T07:20:18.000Z","msg":"爸爸<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69756f42fe96adf7a7e5fbdc013e97b26dcb6f69","tid":510124,"uid":1377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T07:28:32.000Z","msg":"懷念爺爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}